=head1 NAME

Locale::RecodeData::EUC_TW

=head1 SYNOPSIS

This module is internal to libintl.  Do not use directly!

=head1 DESCRIPTION

The base for this module is generated and contains the conversion 
tables and routines for EUC-TW.

EUC-TW is a multi-byte encoding!
